This directory contains the BUILD.Gn file that has been modified to add the OptigaM Files to the build system.

The BUILD.Gn file at the following location should be modified:

/connectedhomeip/third_party/mbedtls

It also contain the mbedtls config.h file with modification to enable HW crypto acceleration. This is at:

/connectedhomeip/third_party/mbedtls/repo/include/mbedtls